    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mechanized devices, typically comprising a chute, packing belt, vibrating plate, and compression roll, used to compress unprocessed fibers and form them into continuous matted sheets. These machines are designed to produce a consistent weight of fiber material required for subsequent carding processes. </Note_Text>
